  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have a micro chakra engine attached to your person. <br />This engine generates a powerful barrier protecting you. <br />This barrier has a number of hit points equal to [Level x 10]. <br />It intercepts all damage this adversary would take and is resistant to all Damage types, except psychic, and is immune to chakra damage. <br />trait can be temporarily deactivated if this adversary is targeted by a special effect such as B-Rank Chakra dispel or Uzumaki Break. <br />You can change the effect or jutsu needed to one your party has such as a specific condition, Action or damage type. <br />This trait is deactivated until the end of this adversaries next turn.</p>",
